#: ../../../../../../../.conda/lib/python3.13/site-packages/numpy/polynomial/chebyshev.py:docstring
#: of numpy.polynomial.chebyshev.chebcompanion:4
msgid ""
"The basis polynomials are scaled so that the companion matrix is symmetric "
"when `c` is a Chebyshev basis polynomial. This provides better eigenvalue "
"estimates than the unscaled case and for basis polynomials the eigenvalues "
"are guaranteed to be real if `numpy.linalg.eigvalsh` is used to obtain them."
msgstr ""

